<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-83-0870 </DOCNO><TEXT>The variety of uses for fluidized beds is discussed. The most prominentapplication is in fluidized bed combustors for power generation but otheruses include water purification; production of chemicals and biochemicals;and maximising the rate of heat transfer in processing plants. Coal andwastes can be burned in fbcs.</TEXT></DOC>